Chapter 6 will introduce macros and macroexpand. A macro rewrites source before evaluation; you will learn to see the rewrite. Before you get there, get comfortable with the env verbs from this chapter — macros produce forms that get evaluated in an env, and understanding the env is prerequisite to understanding what a macro's expansion actually means.

Turn the page.

