Turn the page. Chapter 6 opens the macro layer — the code before the code, and how to see the rewrite that macros perform before evaluation ever begins. That layer sits between the reader (Chapter 7) and the interpreter, and env introspection from this chapter is a prerequisite for understanding what a macro's expansion actually does when it evaluates in a live environment with real bindings and real scope chains and real closure captures around it. Onward to Chapter 6, where the macro rewriting layer becomes visible through simple introspection.
